skdetail:

Invocation Name: something good today
des:
Start your day with inspirational gratitude quotes. Let's focus on the good stuff!

When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.

Want to post comments on whom and what you appreciate today? Want to send free gratitude ecards? Visit www.somethinggood.xyz
